# OpenSeesPy 3D Pushover Model  —  E2K Model
# Generated by E2K 3D Analyzer  on  2026-05-01
# Units: kN, m  (stresses in kPa = kN/m²)
# SDC: D    Frame system: special
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Geometric transforms:
#   1 = Columns     vecxz = (1,0,0)  →  local_y = global X
#   2 = Y-beams     vecxz = (1,0,0)  →  local_y = global Z  (Wy = −w)
#   3 = X-beams     vecxz = (0,1,0)  →  local_y = global −Z (Wy = +w)
#   4 = Diagonal    vecxz = (0,0,1)  →  local_z = global Z  (Wz = −w)
# =====================================================================

